        Categories
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div
      id="panelsStayOpen-collapseThird"
      class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
      aria-labelledby="panelsStayOpen-headingThird"
    >
      <div class="accordion-body">
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="mb-3">
